Class DataVisibility

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dgfoundation.amp.visibility.data.DataVisibility
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ColumnsVisibility, GenericVisibility, MeasuresVisibility, ModulesVisibility, RuleBasedVisibility

    public abstract class DataVisibility
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides common support for visibility detection, at the moment for report columns and measures.
